00:09:32.238 --> 00:09:33.973  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[boy 1] Damn...

141
00:09:34.040 --> 00:09:36.809  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
If we'd caught him, then we could
have gotten a hundred million yen.

142
00:09:36.876 --> 00:09:38.844  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[boy 2] If we'd known about it
beforehand...

143
00:09:38.911 --> 00:09:43.015  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[boy 1] If only he'd died when we were
the only ones around.

144
00:09:43.082 --> 00:09:44.650  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[boy 2 chuckles]

145
00:09:44.717 --> 00:09:47.587  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So, what are we gonna do
about our Physics homework?

146
00:09:47.653 --> 00:09:49.989  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-We always got it off Nagai.
-Oh!

147
00:09:50.056 --> 00:09:52.692  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yeah, I guess
that's the worst thing about this.

148
00:09:52.758 --> 00:09:56.329  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[both laughing]

149
00:09:58.230 --> 00:10:00.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What, something wrong?

150
00:10:01.601 --> 00:10:03.035  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's nothing.

151
00:10:04.770 --> 00:10:07.607  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Stop quibbling. Just do your job.

152
00:10:07.673 --> 00:10:08.941  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
But, Mr. Araki...

153
00:10:09.008 --> 00:10:14.246  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Huh? Didn't I just say,
I'm not asking for your opinion?

154
00:10:15.715 --> 00:10:19.185  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I guess that's as much as we can expect
from the local police.

155
00:10:19.251 --> 00:10:21.354  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
What about applying
the Ajin Protection Law?

156
00:10:21.621 --> 00:10:23.923  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The pursuit requires manpower.

157
00:10:26.025 --> 00:10:28.861  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We don't want them turning against us.

158
00:10:28.928 --> 00:10:32.031  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Don't interfere.
-Yes, sir.

159
00:10:32.298 --> 00:10:33.799  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Araki] Um...

160
00:10:33.866 --> 00:10:35.635  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm sorry to interrupt you.

161
00:10:35.701 --> 00:10:38.070  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-What is it?
-Well...

162
00:10:38.137 --> 00:10:41.273  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It'd really be helpful to know
a bit more about Ajins

163
00:10:41.340 --> 00:10:44.343  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
in order to capture it
as quickly as possible.

164
00:11:00.059 --> 00:11:01.761  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[muffled crying]

165
00:11:03.329 --> 00:11:05.765  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hey, what are you doing?

166
00:11:06.198 --> 00:11:09.268  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[thug 1] Shut up. Just look straight ahead
and drive, jerk.

167
00:11:09.335 --> 00:11:12.438  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[thug 2] Are you really sure
it was the Ajin?

168
00:11:12.705 --> 00:11:15.141  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I told you, I'm sure of it.

169
00:11:23.749 --> 00:11:25.818  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Kai.
-Huh?

170
00:11:25.885 --> 00:11:29.688  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I know it's not a good time, but I...

171
00:11:30.256 --> 00:11:31.991  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Well, I really have to pee.

172
00:11:32.958 --> 00:11:35.261  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh. Okay, let's find a side street.

173
00:12:01.821 --> 00:12:02.988  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[sighs]

174
00:12:03.222 --> 00:12:05.324  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>So, pee comes out normally.</i>

175
00:12:05.391 --> 00:12:06.992  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>I guess that makes sense.</i>

176
00:12:07.059 --> 00:12:10.729  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>I lived a normal life</i>
<i>until today after all.</i>

177
00:12:11.797 --> 00:12:13.132  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps, then grunts]

178
00:12:15.134 --> 00:12:16.836  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[thug 1 chuckles]

179
00:12:23.275 --> 00:12:24.410  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh...

180
00:12:29.014 --> 00:12:30.783  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei grunting]

181
00:12:30.850 --> 00:12:32.218  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei?!

182
00:12:36.088 --> 00:12:37.323  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Well?!

183
00:12:39.225 --> 00:12:42.828  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Holy shit, it really is the Ajin!
Holy shit!

184
00:12:42.895 --> 00:12:46.098  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Seriously?! I can't believe it?!
A hundred million yen!

185
00:12:46.165 --> 00:12:50.069  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
We're rich! Holy shit, we're rich!
Oh, my God!

186
00:12:50.136 --> 00:12:51.837  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Who the hell are you?!

187
00:12:52.471 --> 00:12:54.340  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Where the hell did you come from?!

188
00:12:57.243 --> 00:13:00.045  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
And who are you? The Ajin's friend?

189
00:13:00.112 --> 00:13:03.115  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
We'll be keeping this Ajin,
just so you know.

190
00:13:03.182 --> 00:13:05.217  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Like hell you will!

191
00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:10.322  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[girl] Is it really an Ajin?

192
00:13:13.259 --> 00:13:14.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

193
00:13:18.898 --> 00:13:20.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

194
00:13:24.069 --> 00:13:27.206  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>No... No!</i>

195
00:13:30.576 --> 00:13:31.977  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei!

196
00:13:33.145 --> 00:13:34.313  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasping]

197
00:13:38.184 --> 00:13:42.154  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Time to see if you really can't die.

198
00:13:42.821 --> 00:13:45.424  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>Why is this happening?</i>

199
00:13:45.491 --> 00:13:47.092  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Why?</i>

200
00:13:49.895 --> 00:13:52.198  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>I didn't do anything wrong!</i>

201
00:13:52.264 --> 00:13:55.267  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[thug 1] Come on!
You can't be killed, right?!

202
00:13:55.334 --> 00:13:57.970  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
How about it!?

203
00:13:58.037 --> 00:13:59.305  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[thug 1 laughs]

204
00:13:59.371 --> 00:14:01.974  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
That hundred mil is mine.

205
00:14:03.375 --> 00:14:06.145  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting] All of you...

206
00:14:08.113 --> 00:14:10.349  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Just die...

207
00:14:11.884 --> 00:14:13.986  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Die...

208
00:14:23.062 --> 00:14:24.530  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh? What?

209
00:14:24.597 --> 00:14:26.599  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
They don't die, right?!

210
00:14:26.866 --> 00:14:28.334  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei!

211
00:14:35.608 --> 00:14:37.509  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why me...?

212
00:14:37.576 --> 00:14:39.178  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why...?

213
00:14:39.245 --> 00:14:41.413  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
No, never mind that.

214
00:14:42.248 --> 00:14:43.415  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

215
00:14:45.284 --> 00:14:46.285  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kei!

216
00:14:47.519 --> 00:14:49.488  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[groaning]

217
00:14:54.093 --> 00:14:58.364  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[thug 1] Hey, this Ajin died!

218
00:14:58.430 --> 00:15:00.099  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>No.</i>

219
00:15:01.233 --> 00:15:02.568  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>I'm...</i>

220
00:15:07.373 --> 00:15:09.575  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[yelling]

221
00:15:14.914 --> 00:15:16.448  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[girl] <i>What's happening?</i>

222
00:15:22.021 --> 00:15:24.189  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kai] <i>My body won't move.</i>

223
00:15:24.623 --> 00:15:26.425  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[panting]

224
00:15:27.393 --> 00:15:29.128  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kei] <i>It's like when I was leaving school.</i>

225
00:15:29.194 --> 00:15:31.697  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>So, this is what this does!</i>

226
00:15:33.232 --> 00:15:34.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunts]

227
00:15:35.267 --> 00:15:36.568  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[groaning]

228
00:15:36.635 --> 00:15:38.604  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Kai, can you stand up?! Let's go!

229
00:15:40.539 --> 00:15:42.341  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasping]

230
00:15:50.516 --> 00:15:52.584  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Tosaki] <i>This part is well known...</i>

231
00:15:53.319 --> 00:15:56.021  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
but beware of an Ajin's voice.

232
00:15:56.088 --> 00:15:58.123  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yes, I've heard of that.

233
00:15:58.190 --> 00:16:01.427  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It's like temporary paralysis
that lasts for a few seconds.

234
00:16:01.493 --> 00:16:03.329  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It does no physical harm,

235
00:16:03.395 --> 00:16:06.165  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
but you must take care
when you're trying to capture them.

236
00:16:10.102 --> 00:16:11.470  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[both grunting]

237
00:16:12.504 --> 00:16:14.373  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[thug 2] You okay?

238
00:16:14.440 --> 00:16:16.508  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Other than getting punched...

239
00:16:16.575 --> 00:16:18.544  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Damn it, we gotta go after them!

240
00:16:20.245 --> 00:16:22.448  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ah! The girl's gone!
-Forget her!

241
00:16:22.514 --> 00:16:24.149  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hurry up, dumbass!

242
00:16:27.219 --> 00:16:28.287  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[engine starts]

243
00:16:28.354 --> 00:16:29.655  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We screwed up!

244
00:16:30.356 --> 00:16:32.658  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
A voice that stops people's movement.

245
00:16:32.725 --> 00:16:34.460  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
That's so strange.

246
00:16:34.526 --> 00:16:36.295  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Do you know how they do it?

247
00:16:36.362 --> 00:16:38.630  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm not at liberty to say.

248
00:16:38.697 --> 00:16:40.232  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Araki sighs]

249
00:16:40.299 --> 00:16:41.467  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Mr. Araki.

250
00:16:42.634 --> 00:16:45.137  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Mr. Toza-- Mr. Tosaki.

251
00:16:45.204 --> 00:16:48.307  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It seems they're done questioning
the mother.

252
00:16:48.374 --> 00:16:49.441  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Tosaki] Well, then...

253
00:16:49.675 --> 00:16:52.244  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Uh... May I ask one thing before that?

254
00:16:52.311 --> 00:16:54.013  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yes?

255
00:16:55.047 --> 00:16:59.618  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You're not hiding anything
about the Ajins, are you?

256
00:17:00.085 --> 00:17:01.553  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Araki chuckles]

257
00:17:01.620 --> 00:17:06.025  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
No, I mean, you hear it all the time,
right? That they're always hiding stuff--

258
00:17:06.091 --> 00:17:08.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I won't say
that we're not hiding anything.

259
00:17:08.627 --> 00:17:12.331  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
But there's nothing other than the voice
that will affect any of you.

260
00:17:13.165 --> 00:17:16.101  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ajins aren't inherently dangerous.
You have my word.

261
00:17:17.269 --> 00:17:19.538  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Well, then, good luck.

262
00:17:19.605 --> 00:17:20.639  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sir.

263
00:17:25.277 --> 00:17:27.246  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We're not human.

264
00:17:29.581 --> 00:17:32.818  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
When we're on duty, we're something else.
We're public officials.

265
00:17:33.085 --> 00:17:36.455  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The more you acknowledge that,
the less sentiment you'll feel.

266
00:17:36.522 --> 00:17:38.223  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Remember that.

267
00:17:40.125 --> 00:17:42.728  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Izumi Shimomura.

268
00:17:42.795 --> 00:17:44.096  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Izumi] Yes, sir.

269
00:17:51.336 --> 00:17:53.739  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Izumi] <i>Ajins aren't inherently dangerous.</i>

270
00:17:55.140 --> 00:17:58.310  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>As long as Kei Nagai isn't a variant.</i>

271
00:18:07.753 --> 00:18:08.821  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

272
00:18:12.424 --> 00:18:15.127  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-What is it?
-Nothing.

273
00:18:15.194 --> 00:18:19.331  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Kei, I'm sorry, I let my guard down.
I didn't think this would happen.

274
00:18:19.398 --> 00:18:22.835  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Don't worry about that.
But you-- You're injured. Ah!

275
00:18:31.777 --> 00:18:33.212  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Damn it.

276
00:18:36.215 --> 00:18:37.382  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We got you!

277
00:18:37.449 --> 00:18:40.185  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Run them over!
It won't actually kill them!

278
00:18:40.252 --> 00:18:41.487  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Got it!

279
00:18:47.793 --> 00:18:51.163  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Are they trying to hit us?!
-They're insane!

280
00:18:52.498 --> 00:18:55.834  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Kei] <i>It's because of you guys that...</i>
<i>Because of you guys...</i>

281
00:18:55.901 --> 00:18:57.803  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Go! Smash them!

282
00:18:58.237 --> 00:18:59.571  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[tires screeching]

283
00:19:02.274 --> 00:19:03.275  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
